&lt;p&gt;
The CUX series low speed type free mount cylinder saves space and allows direct and precise mounting. It is available in 10mm to 32mm bore sizes with stroke lengths up to 50mm. Specifications include, double acting single rod, non-lube type cylinder, double side rubber bumpers and basic type mounting.
&lt;/p&gt;

